 Lupe Fiasco 分享了之前未发行的儿童叛军歌曲《Shrink》，收录了 Radiohead 样本https://www.nme.com/news/music/lupe-fiasco-shares-previously-unreleased-child-rebel-soldier-song-shrink-featuring-radiohead-sample-3783895?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=lupe-惨败分享之前未发行的儿童叛军士兵歌曲缩小以电台头样本为特色Surej SinghThu, 15 Aug 2024 05:59:20 +0000 Music NewsNewsRap https://www.nme.com/?p=3783895 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/lupe-fiasco-radiohead@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Lupe Fiasco 和 Radiohead 的 Thom Yorke" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/lupe-fiasco-radiohead@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/lupe-fiasco-radiohead@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/lupe-fiasco-radiohead@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/lupe-fiasco-radiohead@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/lupe-fiasco-radiohead@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/lupe-fiasco-radiohead@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这首歌曲最初是为这位说唱歌手与 Kanye West 和 Pharrell Williams 组成的超级组合而创作，并采样了 Radiohead 的《Optimistic》</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lupe-fiasco-shares-previously-unreleased-child-rebel-soldier-song-shrink-featuring-radiohead-sample-3783895">Lupe Fiasco 发布的帖子分享了之前未发行的儿童叛军士兵歌曲“Shrink”，其中收录了 Radiohead 样本，该歌曲</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/lupe-fiasco-radiohead@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Lupe Fiasco 和 Radiohead 的 Thom Yorke" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/lupe-fiasco-radiohead@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/lupe-fiasco-radiohead@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/lupe-fiasco-radiohead@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/lupe-fiasco-radiohead@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/lupe-fiasco-radiohead@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/lupe-fiasco-radiohead@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lupe-fiasco">Lupe Fiasco</a>分享了《Shrink》，这是一首之前未发行的儿童叛军歌曲，其中包含<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/radiohead">Radiohead</a>样本 - 请在下面查看。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/the-smile-london-hammersmith-apollo-radiohead-review-setlist-photos-3599692">The Smile 伦敦现场演出：Radiohead 在全新世界中的爵士朋克冒险</a></strong></li></ul><p>《Shrink》收录了 Radiohead 的《Optimistic》样本，取自《Kid A》。这首歌是与 Child Rebel Soldier (CRS) 共同创作的，该乐队是 Lupe Fiasco 与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kanye-west">Kanye West</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pharrell-williams">Pharrell Williams</a>组成的前超级组合。然而，《Shrink》中没有 Kanye 或 Pharrell 的参与，而是由 Lupe 用他的声音重新录制了这首歌。</p><p>听下面的“收缩”。 </p><p><iframe title="CRS-“收缩”" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/SysarGaw1q8?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Lupe Fiasco 在 7 月份<a href="https://www.stereogum.com/2271933/weve-got-a-file-on-you-lupe-fiasco/interviews/weve-got-a-file-on-you/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">向<em>Stereogum</em>透露</a>，他的目标是重启 CRS 作为一个个人项目，重点是他对 Radiohead 样本的说唱，这也是 Kanye West 和 Pharrell 参与之前的最初打算。</p><p> Fiasco 谈到 CRS 的现状时说道：“人们一直把它放在我身上，就像是，‘嘿，这不是我。’”法雷尔在路易威登，叶则在某个该死的工厂里生产袜子。所以[现在]，我想他妈的，我将在接下来的六个月内重新启动 CRS，也许明年，但它会回到原来的能量，那就是我在 Radiohead 的节拍上说唱。” </p><figure id="attachment_3477874" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3477874" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3477874" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/lupe-fiasco-tim-mosen.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/lupe-fiasco-tim-mosen.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/lupe-fiasco-tim-mosen-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/lupe-fiasco-tim-mosen-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/lupe-fiasco-tim-mosen-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/lupe-fiasco-tim-mosen-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/lupe-fiasco-tim-mosen-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3477874" class="wp-caption-text">图片来源：蒂姆·莫森菲尔德/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>在《Shrink》之前，CRS 已经发行了两首歌曲：2007 年的《Us Placers》和 2010 年的《Don&#39;t Stop》。《Us Placers》看到了乐队样本<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/thom-yorke">Thom Yorke</a>的《The Eraser》。 Lupe Fiasco 过去还在“Animal Pharm”中采样了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/atoms-for-peace">Atoms For Peace</a>的“Ingenue”，在“National Anthem Freestyle”中采样了 Radiohead 的“National Anthem”。</p><p>然而，《Shrink》不会是最后一首包含 Thom Yorke 项目样本的 CRS 音乐。他向<em>Stereogum</em>解释道：“你可以把这些唱片，《国歌》唱片、《Us Placers》和《Animal Pharm》作为前三张单曲。你可能还会得到另外五六个。我们会看到的。”</p><p> Lupe Fiasco 最近于六月底发行了他的最新专辑《Samurai》。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lupe-fiasco-shares-previously-unreleased-child-rebel-soldier-song-shrink-featuring-radiohead-sample-3783895">Lupe Fiasco 发布的帖子分享了之前未发行的儿童叛军士兵歌曲“Shrink”，其中收录了 Radiohead 样本，该歌曲</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
